    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6692450/" class="title-link">历史悬疑小说，不是谁都拿得起</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6692450"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/48811776/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u48811776-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48811776/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">最后的武士</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-06-04"
      class="main-meta">2014-06-04 23:37:43</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6692450_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  比较糟糕的一部小说，不可否认，作者在写作之初查阅了很多的历史资料，但很遗憾地，这些资料从未融入到小说。只是很粗糙和不合时宜的罗列，读起来丝毫没有汲取知识的快感，反倒有种对略显卖弄的反感。  再说说剧情，非常离散，前边的剧情松散，后边又故作紧张，而且所有的出场...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6692450_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6692450_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










